improved_metadata.title: Foam in the Middle: Home Insulation Guide
improved_metadata.description: This song humorously explains the benefits of home insulation using foam, advising listeners to properly insulate their homes to stay cool and avoid high energy bills. It offers a lighthearted take on a practical home improvement topic.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Build your walls and put foam in the middle, keep the channel circumference
